      "content": "hey just had a question about my warfarin. i've been on 5mg for a while now and i honestly feel great. like super healthy and nothing is wrong. i was thinking of maybe dropping down to 2mg just to see if i can maintain it with a lower dose? feels like i might not even need the full 5mg anymore if i'm doing well.",
