      "content": "i hear you but i'm just really frustrated with the wait times. i just want to feel like i have some control over my own health. if i were to just do a gradual taper instead of jumping straight there, like maybe 3mg or 4mg for a bit, would that be a safer way to ease into a lower dose? i just don't want to stay on such a high dose if i don't actually need it anymore.",
